resource.title: Treatment plan for chronic kidney disease stage 4
resource.description: Comprehensive treatment plan including AV Fistula Surgery, Hemodialysis Sessions, Medication Management

resource.conclusion: Patient shows stable status for chronic kidney disease stage 4. Sakura Nguyen, a 35-year-old Asian female diagnosed with severe chronic kidney disease stage 4, initiated hemodialysis treatment on 2010-04-15. The treatment included AV fistula surgery followed by multiple dialysis sessions with medication management. The patient's current status is stable with regular follow-up visits for medication adjustments and lab tests.
